Quote:  <i>like a maggot on a hot plate</i> incessant wriggling about; eg `After three hours of listening to <i>Die Walku"re on the hideously uncomfortable wooden seats, he was beside himself with restlessness, like a maggot on a hot plate.' <i>[Jim Henderson] </i>
